    "Based on my analysis of the codebase, here are the APIs integrated in this Solana wallet tracker project:\n\n## **Integrated APIs**\n\n### **1. Helius API** (Primary - Required)\n- **Endpoint**: `https://mainnet.helius-rpc.com/` & `https://api.helius.xyz/v0/transactions/`\n- **Uses**:\n  - Real-time wallet transaction monitoring via WebSocket\n  - Enhanced transaction parsing with human-readable descriptions\n  - DAS (Digital Asset Standard) for token metadata\n  - Mint/freeze authority verification\n  - Round-robin load balancing across multiple API keys\n- **Features**: Supports multiple API keys (HELIUS_API_KEY, HELIUS_API_KEY1-99) for higher throughput\n\n### **2. Moralis API** (Recommended)\n- **Endpoint**: `https://solana-gateway.moralis.io/token/mainnet/`\n- **Uses**:\n  - Token metadata (name, symbol, decimals)\n  - Real-time price data (USD/SOL)\n  - DEX pairs and liquidity information\n  - Top holders data\n- **Features**: Free tier available, replaces GMGN which was blocked by Cloudflare\n\n### **3. Pump.fun API**\n- **Endpoint**: `https://frontend-api-v3.pump.fun/coins/`\n- **Uses**:\n  - Detect Pump.fun token launches\n  - Bonding curve status\n  - Token metadata for Pump.fun tokens\n  - Market cap and trading data\n- **Features**: Custom headers to bypass bot detection\n\n### **4. DexScreener API** (Free)\n- **Endpoint**: `https://api.dexscreener.com/latest/dex/tokens/`\n- **Uses**:\n  - Real-time DEX pair data\n  - Price, volume, liquidity metrics\n  - LP burn status\n  - Social links (Twitter, Telegram, website)\n  - 24h price changes\n- **Features**: No API key required\n\n### **5. RugCheck API** (Free)\n- **Endpoint**: `https://api.rugcheck.xyz/v1/tokens/`\n- **Uses**:\n  - Security verification (mint/freeze authority)\n  - Risk score calculation\n  - LP lock percentage\n  - Top holders analysis\n  - Rug pull detection\n- **Features**: Comprehensive security analysis without authentication\n\n### **6. Jupiter Price API** (Free)\n- **Endpoint**: Referenced in test files for price verification\n- **Uses**:\n  - Token price validation\n  - Cross-reference pricing data\n- **Features**: Aggregated DEX pricing\n\n### **7. GMGN API** (Optional)\n- **Endpoint**: `https://gmgn.ai/defi/quotation/v1/`\n- **Uses**:\n  - Smart wallet tracking\n  - Trading signals and buy pressure\n  - Dev wallet history (rug detection)\n  - Hot level indicators\n- **Features**: Can be accessed via Apify actor if direct API is blocked\n\n### **8. Birdeye API** (Optional)\n- **Endpoint**: Token metadata and market data\n- **Uses**:\n  - Additional price verification\n  - Trading volume data\n  - Holder count validation\n- **Features**: Requires API key\n\n### **9. CoinGecko API** (Free)\n- **Endpoint**: `https://api.coingecko.com/api/v3/simple/price`\n- **Uses**:\n  - SOL/USD price conversion\n  - Market data reference\n- **Features**: No authentication required\n\n### **10. Solana RPC** (Custom/Public)\n- **Endpoint**: Configurable via `RPC_ENDPOINTS` env variable\n- **Uses**:\n  - On-chain data verification\n  - Token account queries\n  - Supply and holder verification\n  - Transaction confirmation\n- **Features**: Supports multiple RPC providers for load balancing\n\n### **11. Telegram Bot API**\n- **Endpoint**: `https://api.telegram.org/bot`\n- **Uses**:\n  - Send transaction notifications\n  - Bot commands handling\n  - Webhook setup for production\n  - Group chat integration\n- **Features**: Polling (dev) or webhook (production) modes\n\n---\n\n## **How APIs Work Together**\n\n### **Transaction Flow**:\n1. **Helius WebSocket** monitors wallet addresses in real-time\n2. When transaction detected → **Helius Enhanced Parser** provides human-readable description\n3. **Transaction Parser** identifies DEX type (Raydium/Jupiter/Pump.fun/PumpSwap)\n4. **Token Analysis Service** fetches comprehensive data:\n   - **Helius DAS** → metadata & authorities\n   - **Moralis** → price, holders, DEX pairs\n   - **DexScreener** → real-time trading data\n   - **RugCheck** → security verification\n   - **Pump.fun API** → bonding curve status (if applicable)\n   - **GMGN** → smart wallet signals (optional)\n5. **Message Builder** formats data with links to trading bots\n6. **Telegram Bot** sends notification to user\n\n### **Data Aggregation Strategy**:\n- **Fallback chain**: If one API fails, falls back to next source\n- **Cross-validation**: Prices verified across multiple sources\n- **Caching**: Reduces redundant API calls\n- **Rate limiting**: Round-robin key rotation for Helius\n- **Optional enhancement**: `ENABLE_ENHANCED_METADATA` flag controls comprehensive analysis\n\n### **Key Features**:\n- ✅ Multi-source data aggregation for accuracy\n- ✅ Automatic failover between API providers\n- ✅ Load balancing with multiple API keys\n- ✅ Real-time WebSocket monitoring\n- ✅ Security analysis (rug detection, authority checks)\n- ✅ Market data (price, volume, liquidity, holders)\n- ✅ Trading bot integration links\n[Tool uses: none]",
